I really like this game. It's fun, and can be quite challenging. But my 
problem is with the actual map itself. The map is, let's say, all over the 
place. I was expecting something more flat for the horses. I don't mean 
that it would be lacking mountains, just that the areas that were meant to 
be flat, would be flat. Their are odd spikes, and bumps everywhere, and the 
map just feels jagged and unpolished compared to everything else which 
feels polished, and fine tuned. It's honestly hard for me to play it with 
the way the map is. However I don't think my problems will ever be fixed, 
seeing as the game hasn't been updated since 2015.
